<br>
Just checked the 2 logs I had used, one a 75 attacks log, the other a 736 attacks compilation of logs. Both showed a critical chance of 14.6% for a skald with MoPain 2. <br>
Unfortunately, the second one was polluted by about 200 attacks from my berserker, who doesn't have MoPain <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  . (I keep log files for both characters, and the berserker is unsuitable for parsing for criticals, for obvious reasons).<br>
Cleaned out, the big log gives me a 19.7% chance for criticals. (And yes, the second one is too small. I had just used it for confirmation, curse my luck).<br>
<br>
So 10% + 5% per level of MoPain.<br>
<br>
Sorry for the confusion. <br>
