<br>
i do not care about your bronze dagger.  how many crits i get with a bronze dagger unstyled on a grey mob i could not care less about.  this game is about rvr, rvr is all i care about.  rvr should be all YOU care about, other than enough pve to fund your purchasing of rams and ironwood to fix doors.<br>
<br>
i will state this one more time, as apparently the two times i have already stated it were insufficient to get my point across.<br>
<br>
IN REALM VERSUS REALM FIGHTING, IN THE TIME IT TOOK MY SKALD TO REACH RANK FIVE (FIVE HUNDRED FIFTEEN THOUSAND REALM POINTS), I DID NOT GET ONE SINGLE CRIT.  NOT ONE.  THAT MEANS ZERO.<br>
<br>
AFTER I PURCHASED MASTERY OF PAIN MY SKALD DID CRIT IN RVR.<br>
<br>
CONCLUSION:  MY SKALD DOES NOT CRIT IN RVR WITHOUT MASTERY OF PAIN.<br>
<br>
thanks for reading, and please comprehend this time.  as it will be the final time.<br>
